do-build:
path = "testsuites/libtests/dl01/"

tar = path + "dl01.tar"

self.link_cc(bld, bic, objs, dl01_pre)
dl01_sym_o = path + "dl01-sym.o"

self.rtems_syms(bld, dl01_pre, dl01_sym_o)
